pe-verdi/" rel="tag">Giuseppe Verdi</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/hugo-de-ana/" rel="tag">Hugo De Ana</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/irena-petkova/" rel="tag">Irena Petkova</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/la-traviata/" rel="tag">La Traviata</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/nathalie-manfrino/" rel="tag">Nathalie Manfrino</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/opera-lirica/" rel="tag">Opera lirica</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/steven-mercurio/" rel="tag">Steven Mercurio</a><meta itemprop="keywords" content="Elia Fabbian, francesco demuro, Gabriele Nani, Giuseppe Verdi, Hugo De Ana, Irena Petkova, La Traviata, Nathalie Manfrino, Opera lirica, Steven Mercurio"> </span> </footer></div> </article><div id="author-block" class="box-shadow-2px clearfix" itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/Person"><h2 class="author-title">About the author</h2><div id="author-avatar"> <img itemprop="image" style="display:none;" src="http://gravatar.com/avatar/06f1dca16cc797d944409356f8080fb9" alt="" /> <img src="http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/06f1dca16cc797d944409356f8080fb9?s=100&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g" width="100" height="100" alt="" class="avatar avatar-100 wp-user-avatar wp-user-avatar-100 photo avatar-default" /></div><div id="author-description" class="padding-20"><meta itemprop="name" content="Antonio Galli"><meta itemprop="url" content=""><p></p><p class="add-author-info"> <a href="#"><i class="icon-facebook-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-twitter-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-google-plus-sign"></i></a></p> <a style="font-size: 11px;" href="http://www.gbopera.it/author/antonio-galli/">View all articles by Antonio Galli</a></div></div><div class="nav-block box-shadow-2px padding-20 clearfix"> <nav class="nav-single"><h3 class="assistive-text">Post navigation</h3> <span class="nav-previous"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/2012/10/salerno-teatro-verdila-gioconda/" rel="prev"><span class="meta-nav">&larr;</span> Salerno, Teatro Verdi:&#8221;La Gioconda&#8221;</a></span> <span class="nav-next"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/2012/10/brescia-teatro-grande-lucia-di-lammermoor/" rel="next">Brescia, Teatro Grande: &#8220;Lucia di Lammermoor&#8221; <span class="meta-nav">&rarr;</span></a></span> </nav><nav class="nav-single-hidden"> <span class="nav-previous"></span> <span class="nav-next"></span><div class="clear"></div> </nav></div><div class="comments-block box-shadow-2px clearfix"><div id="comments" class="comments-area"><h2 class="comments-title"> 1 comment</h2><ol class="commentlist"><li class="comment even thread-even depth-1" id="li-comment-15797"> <article id="comment-15797" class="comment clearfix"> <header class="comment-meta comment-author vcard"><div class="comment-avatar"><img src="http://1.gravatar.com/avatar/d76f38aface0f75d51c8fa91412fa248?s=75&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g" width="75" height="75" alt="" class="avatar avatar-75wp-user-avatar wp-user-avatar-75 alignnone photo avatar-default" /></div><cite class="fn">rigoletto1</cite><a class="comment-meta-time muted-small" href="http://www.gbopera.it/2012/10/padova-teatro-verdila-traviata/#comment-15797"><time datetime="2012-10-31T12:43:38+00:00">31 ottobre 2012 at 12:43</time></a> </header> <section class="comment-content comment"><p>Lo spettacolo è stato splendido specialmente per il bravissimo Elia Fabbian e per l&#8217;usuale intelligenza ed eleganza di De Ana.<br /> Grazie al Verdi per quello che ci ha offerto!</p> </section><div class="reply clearfix"></div> </article></li></ol><div id="respond" class="comment-respond"><h3 id="reply-title" class="comment-reply-title">Lascia un commento <small><a rel="nofollow" id="cancel-comment-reply-link" href="/2012/10/padova-teatro-verdila-traviata/#respond" style="display:none;">Annulla risposta</a></small></h3><form action="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-comments-post.php" method="post" id="commentform" class="comment-form"><p class="comment-notes"><span id="email-notes">Il tuo indirizzo email non sar